description:
Purchasing this item will add “Round Announcements - 13 Character Set” to MELTY BLOOD: TYPE LUMINA.
This set includes voices for Shiki Tohno, Arcueid, Ciel, Akiha Tohno, Hisui, Kohaku, Noel, Vlov, Roa, Red Arcueid, Kouma Kishima, Miyako Arima, and Saber.
name: DLC: Round Announcements - 13 Character Set
